mpacts so that we can then target certain practices and/or processes to women (or men) farmers.\r\n\r\nAt least 8 of the practices were chosen as priorities by women\'s focus groups in Lushoto, Tanzania.', '', '13', '18', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('433', null, null, '1', '', '', '13', '19', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('434', '1', null, '0', 'The CCAFS gender survey (Phase 2) has been designed to assess the likely gender-disaggregated impact of various CSA practices.  The assessment has not been done yet but is planned in Uganda and Cauca for 2015.  We should be able to assess at least 5 of CSA practices.', '', '13', '19', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('435', null, null, '5', '', '', '13', '20', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('436', '5', null, '', '', '', '13', '20', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('437', null, null, '5000000', '', '', '13', '21', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('438', '5000000', null, '', '', '', '13', '21', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('439', null, null, '1', 'BNI', '', '13', '22', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('440', '1', null, '', '', '', '13', '22', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('441', null, null, '2', '', '', '13', '23', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('442', '2', null, '', '', '', '13', '23', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('443', null, null, '0', '', '', '13', '24', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('444', '1', null, '', '', '', '13', '24', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('445', null, null, '20', '', '', '13', '25', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('446', '25', null, '', '', '', '13', '25', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('447', null, null, '1', 'Brachearia', '', '13', '26', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('448', '1', null, '', '', '', '13', '26', '2014', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('449', 'continued', null, '10', '', '', '13', '27', '2013', '2014-01-28 19:41:03'), ('450', '15', null, '', 'FS4-LAM Gender activity analyzed El Salvador\'s Climate Change policiy for the Ministry of Agriculture to make suggestions/gu