ific interventions when planning for climate smart coffee/cocoa. \r\nThe shade tree advise tool takes into consideration specific needs of farmers, including women.', '1', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('394', '142', '172', '2015', '', 'Innovative methods: ranking analysis for shade tree preferences us local knowledge. \r\nStudy on local knowledge on pests and diseases and comparison with expert knowledge and measurements in the field on Mount Elgon, Uganda\r\nCustomised decision support tools: Shade tree advise tool.', '', 'The shade tree advise tool takes into consideration specific needs of farmers, including women.', '1', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('395', '142', '173', '2016', 'Results from project feed into district-level learning alliances that function as advisory committees to the district technical committees', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('396', '142', '171', '2016', 'Suitability maps are used as base for participatory mapping at district level.', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('397', '142', '172', '2016', 'PhD studies analyse trade-offs at plot level in coffee systems', 'We developed a systems framework that will have coffee/cocoa sector to plan for climate smart coffee/cocoa regions.', '', 'Gender is mentioned in the framework as an important \"factor\" in order to for example increase adoption of CSA technologies.', '1', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('398', '142', '173', '2017', '', null, '', null, '0', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('399', '142', '171', '2017', '', null, '', null, '0', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', ''), ('400', '142', '172', '2017', '', null, '', null, '0', '2015-11-12 13:52:37', '271', '271', '');
