minate information about CSA investment choices that can be used by at least 3 member companies in WBCSD LCTPi', null, '- Gender included in monitoring and evaluation of private sector CSA actions under WBCSD LCTPi workstream', null, '1', '2015-11-13 13:39:19', '132', '132', ''), ('587', '124', '178', '2017', '', null, '', null, '0', '2015-11-13 13:39:19', '132', '132', ''), ('588', '124', '179', '2017', '', null, '', null, '0', '2015-11-13 13:39:19', '132', '132', ''), ('589', '221', '173', '2019', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('590', '221', '171', '2019', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('591', '221', '172', '2019', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('592', '221', '173', '2015', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('593', '221', '171', '2015', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('594', '221', '172', '2015', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('595', '221', '173', '2016', 'N2Africa developed an innovative ‘development to research\' (D2R) model utilizing large scale dissemination and delivery (D&D) campaigns with strong monitoring and evaluation (M&E) feedback, providing the basis for ‘feedback learning loops’ that enable continuous improvement in dissemination and legume technologies.', null, 'Empowering women with legume technologies had greater impact on increasing legume consumption and dietary diversity – key indicators of nutritional impacts – than when legume technologies were extended to men.', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('596', '221', '171', '2016', 'This (GL x GR) x E x M interaction forms the core of our approach, embedded in farming systems analysis to target legume technologies to the heterogeneous farming conditions of smallholder farmers, including the wide diversity of farmers’ access to production resources.', null, 'Specifically address food and nutrition security of the poor, with a strong gender dimension, through legume intensification (with a major focus on double-cropping, intercropping and climbing beans on small farms). Invest in opportunites to ensure equitable participation and engagement, targeting labour-saving interventions for women, adding value at household level.', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('597', '221', '172', '2016', 'N2Africa developed an innovative ‘development to research\' (D2R) model utilizing large scale dissemination and delivery (D&D) campaigns with strong monitoring and evaluation (M&E) feedback, providing the basis for ‘feedback learning loops’ that enable continuous improvement in dissemination and legume technologies.', null, 'Empowering women with legume technologies had greater impact on increasing legume consumption and dietary diversity – key indicators of nutritional impacts – than when legume technologies were extended to men.', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('598', '221', '173', '2017', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('599', '221', '171', '2017', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', ''), ('600', '221', '172', '2017', '', null, '', null, '1', '2015-11-13 14:06:08', '271', '271', '');
