, 'The review of current policy and institutional framework and CSA initiatives has assessed a potential of inclusion of gender and social issues in the CSA scaling up/out plans and programs at national, sub-national and local levels.', '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1015', '61', '173', '2015', '', 'This project has developed CSV development framework, inventory of climate smart interventions including CSA practices and technologies and laid outline for scaling up and implementation plan. The project has also collected primary and secondary information to develop business and institutional models of CSV approach.', '', 'Gender segregated data are collected', '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1016', '61', '171', '2015', '', 'Several CSA technologies and practices were identified and prioritized based on location specific climatic risks and stakeholders priorities (particularly farmers and local agriculture development offices). Pilot studies have started in collaboration with farmers, local governments, agricultural offices in different agro-ecological zones.', '', 'CSA technologies and practices that could be relevant for gender and small/marginal farmers were identified and included in the pilot studies in the different agro-ecological zones.', '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1017', '61', '172', '2015', '', 'Primary and secondary data were collected for developing business models including bio-physical, socio-economic and trade-off analyses.', '', 'Gender segregated data were collected to provide inputs into the business and institutional models of scaling out CSA/CSVs. .', '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1018', '61', '177', '2015', '', 'Several high level engagements and communication meetings with key stakeholders of CSA/CSV have been done. Several capacity building training on designing, implementation and M&E of CSA/CSV program at sub-national and local level were conducted. Baseline survey and CSA prioritization activities were also conducted.', '', 'Gender and social issues were included in the project design, implementation and M&E framework.', '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1019', '61', '40', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1020', '61', '176', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1021', '61', '173', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1022', '61', '171', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1023', '61', '172', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1024', '61', '177', '2016', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 03:47:36', '21', '21', ''), ('1025', '60', '176', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 07:13:46', '878', '878', ''), ('1026', '60', '177', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 07:13:46', '878', '878', ''), ('1027', '7', '176', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 09:23:29', '178', '178', ''), ('1028', '7', '178', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 09:23:29', '178', '178', ''), ('1029', '81', '171', '2019', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 10:36:33', '143', '143', ''), ('1030', '81', '172', '2019', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 10:36:33', '143', '143', ''), ('1031', '81', '171', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 10:36:33', '143', '143', ''), ('1032', '81', '172', '2014', '', null, '', null, '1', '2016-02-25 10:36:33', '143', '143', ''), ('1033', '81', '171', '2015', '', 'Future suitability maps will allow to select the best sources of tree planting materials; these can also be used within CSA.', '', 'Selected priority species can benefit a wide range of endusers, including women, youth and marginalized communities.', '1', '2016-02-25 10:36:33', '143', '143', ''), ('1034', '81', '172', '2015', '', 'Future seed zonation maps are available as a decision-support tool to be used in the Google Eart