, '243', '243', ''), ('7416', null, null, null, '2015', '167', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7417', '4', 'National and subnational policies and implementation mechanisms put in place to regulate genetic resources access and benefit sharing, and to empower national policy actors (including communities) to acquire genetic resources for climate change adaptation. [for 2017-2018, which is final year of the project]', 'State recognition of local community right to participate in decision making regarding the conservation and exploitation of genetic resources. Local community develop access and benefit sharing protocols. Women included in local community committees to consider access applications.', '2016', '167', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7418', '', '[Project ends in 2016]', '', '2017', '167', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7419', '', '[Project ends in 2016]', '', '2019', '167', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7420', null, null, null, '2015', '167', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7421', '1', 'The African Union will develop/adopt guidelines for mutually supportive implementation of the ITPGRFA and Nagoya Protocol, strengthening capacity for climate change adaptation through access and benefit sharing regulation', 'The guidelines will encourage African AU member states to put systems in place that reflect recognition of the right of local communities -- and wormen within those communities -- to participate in decision making concerning access to and management of genetic diversity and sharing benefits associated with their use by others.', '2016', '167', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7422', '', '[Project ends in 2016]', '', '2017', '167', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-28 12:56:14', '243', '243', ''), ('7423', '', '', '', '2019', '173', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 07:13:30', '108', '108', 'erroneous entry'), ('7424', null, null, null, '2015', '173', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 07:13:30', '108', '108', 'erroneous entry'), ('7425', '1', 'The implementation standards developed for AWD in each of the 4 countries are targeted to always reduce GHG emissions by 30%', 'Women will be involved  in information dissemination of site-specific AWD', '2016', '173', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 07:13:30', '108', '108', 'erroneous entry'), ('7426', '', '', '', '2017', '173', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 07:13:30', '108', '108', 'erroneous entry'), ('7427', '', '', '', '2019', '185', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 07:31:01', '108', '108', ''), ('7428', null, null, '', '2015', '185', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 07:31:01', '108', '108', ''), ('7429', '0', 'Project will only start mid 2016', 'All activities will be implemented with particular consideration of gender implications.', '2016', '185', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 07:31:01', '108', '108', ''), ('7430', '', '', '', '2017', '185', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 07:31:01', '108', '108', ''), ('7431', '1', 'Two NGOS are beginning to use evidence on climate smartness of water storage options to prioritise and inform the implementation of their capacity building programmes. One NGO has also begun to use manuals, info-graphics and other materials produced through this project’s work in their activities, localizing and translating where appropriate. 50,000 farmers are sensitized on the benefits of water storage options through these activities. This has resulted in 500 CSV farmers and 5000 beyond the CSVs, implementing additional water storage options on their farms.', 'At least 50% of the prioritised storage options are specifically targeting women and youth. At least 50% of the sensitised farmers are women and youth.', '2017', '38', '13', '53', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 08:15:54', '94', '94', ''), ('7432', '0', 'At least one NGO is actively developing new (or expanding existing to include), financing choices for farmers relating to water storage options in their credit provision schemes. At least 50 farmers within the CSVs have (through this new offering and the farmer’s involvement in the project’s capacity building and workshop activities) then taken up this credit scheme option to develop a water storage option. 5,000 farmers have access to the credit scheme for investing in water storage options.', 'At least 50% of the farmers receiving credit are women and youth. Credit schemes are particularly targeting women and youth.', '2017', '38', '14', '53', null, null, null, '0', '2015-10-29 08:15:54', '94', '94', ''), ('7433', '', '', '', '2019', '182', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 08:31:29', '108', '108', ''), ('7434', null, null, '', '2015', '182', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 08:31:29', '108', '108', ''), ('7435', '0.01', 'Outscaling of AWD in Central Luzon', 'Gender questions are fully integrated in the project', '2016', '182', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 08:31:29', '108', '108', ''), ('7436', '', '', '', '2017', '182', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-29 08:31:29', '108', '108', ''), ('7437', '', '', '', '2019', '187', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-30 07:01:48', '108', '108', ''), ('7438', null, null, null, '2015', '187', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-30 07:01:48', '108', '108', ''), ('7439', '1', 'The implementation standards developed for AWD in each of the 4 countries are targeted to always reduce GHG emissions by 30%', 'Women will be involved  in information dissemination of site-specific AWD', '2016', '187', '38', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-10-30 07:01:48', '108', '108', ''), ('7440', '', '', '', '2017'