omes at scale, based on CCSL evidence. Linkages with organisations like CSIRO and DFID, through the evidence base work conducted by IIED are potential pathways towards outcomes.', 'Social learning is inherently about social inclusion - i.e. about power relations, equity concerns and including all stakeholders in the process of social learning.', '2017', '62', '52', '25', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 11:37:19', '5', '5', ''), ('7462', '0', 'Project ends in 2017', null, '2019', '191', '50', '55', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 11:51:33', '82', '915', ''), ('7463', '0', null, null, '2015', '191', '50', '55', '0.00', 'The project is still in its early stages and no relevant results can be reported at this stage.', 'The project is still in its early stages and no relevant results can be reported at this stage.', '1', '2015-11-04 11:51:33', '82', '915', ''), ('7464', '0', 'there will be no outcome in 2016', 'The project conducts a socially differentiated analysis of determinants of adaptive capacity and access to governance institutions.', '2016', '191', '50', '55', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 11:51:33', '82', '915', ''), ('7465', '1', '6)  Provide a decision-support tool that helps local partners, USAID and decision-maker take better informed decisions regarding the types of policies, investments, and interventions most likely to be successful in different ecological and socio-economic conditions.', 'The project conducts a socially differentiated analysis of determinants of adaptive capacity and access to governance institutions.', '2017', '191', '50', '55', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 11:51:33', '82', '915', ''), ('7466', '1', 'We will begin support for the Tanzania LED process in 2017 and hope to have evidence of this.', 'as for 2016.', '2017', '12', '38', '69', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 12:25:56', '82', '82', ''), ('7467', '', '', '', '2019', '184', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 13:06:43', '243', '243', ''), ('7468', n