heir local development plans.', 'Learning Alliance members including men, women and youth will participate in the formulation process of these policies', '2017', '6', '50', '70', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 13:57:48', '173', '173', ''), ('7484', '', '', '', '2019', '181', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7485', null, null, '', '2015', '181', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7486', '', '', '', '2016', '181', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7487', '', '', '', '2017', '181', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7488', '', '', '', '2019', '181', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7489', null, null, '', '2015', '181', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7490', '', '', '', '2016', '181', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7491', '', '', '', '2017', '181', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-04 15:06:42', '243', '243', ''), ('7492', '3', 'Experiment in each country to foster district level decision-makers, civil society organizations, regional organizations to make use of CCAFS science-derived decision support tools and systems to mainstream climate change into district plans and policies', 'In each district-platform the different social groups are represented. The process is open and inclusive in order to capture the diversity that exists in each community in the policy cycle.', '2017', '1', '50', '55', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 17:41:29', '199', '199', ''), ('7493', '5', 'Through Bilaterals in addition to institutions in Colombia, Nicaragua and Peru, we will involve 4 more institutions:  Argentinian national institute for agriculture technology (INTA) and the Uruguayan rice growers association (ACA). FLAR as continent-wide rice growers association with all their partners will benefit of the CSMS .FLAR is a public-private alliance investing in a common platform for rice development.Our partners have different needs and capacities since each of them are deferentially advanced in data availability on rice production. Colombia can be considered with high data availability, Nicaragua medium and Peru low due to weakness of institutions', 'Women from two communities in Nicaragua, use gender-site specific reports improving the adaptation of rice productive systems to climate variability and change.', '2017', '58', '13', '108', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-04 20:17:10', '54', '54', ''), ('7494', '60', 'Activity 2014-232:  11 villages (covered by 2 sub-national governments) are demonstrating on-the-ground scalable CSA practices & are engaged in CBA and local adaptation planning; with well-developed proof-of-concept sites used as learning venues by local governments,  researchers, farmers’ networks, and academe on CSA, CBA & local adaptation planning. \r\n\r\nActivity 2014-233: 60 villages have been reached by farmer-centered extension interventions that aim to scale out CSA and CBA. 18 of these villages are scaling-out (expansion) areas. local governments of these villages are also engaged in local adaptation planning that utilize project-derived knowledge products.', 'Women groups in at least 29 villages are directly contributing to local governments\' adaptation planning processes; wherein projects & interventions that promote increased access to and greater control of production assets are drawn and supported by private and public funds.', '2017', '55', '13', '87', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 05:01:46', '871', '871', ''), ('7495', '11', 'Activity 2014-232: 11 villages (covered by 2 subnational governments) have mature experience on the modalities for expediting CSA adoption & CBA through a \"community innovations fund\".', 'Interim knowledge products generated on \"community innovations fund\" as an incentive mechanism to address climate-induced gender issues/concerns.', '2017', '55', '14', '88', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 05:01:46', '871', '871', ''), ('7496', '1', 'CCAFS techniques and tools will be disseminated through national and international meetings/workshops, journal articles', 'Not applicable', '2017', '113', '13', '13', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 08:36:53', '193', '193', ''), ('7497', '1', 'At least 1 national institutes and/or private companies/enterprises will be involved in developing new incentive mechanisms for promoting CSA practices', 'Social organizations (farmer union, women union, youth union, etc.) are willing to participate in CCAFS activities', '2017', '113', '14', '14', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 08:36:53', '193', '193', ''), ('7498', '', '', '', '2019', '202', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:12:36', '82', '86', ''), ('7499', null, null, null, '2015', '202', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:12:36', '82', '86', ''), ('7500', '', '', '', '2016', '202', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:12:36', '82', '86', ''), ('7501', '', '', '', '2017', '202', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:12:36', '82', '86', ''), ('7502', '2', 'The Kenya Dairy NAMA (see 2016).  The LED strategy for livestock in Tanzania will be informed by the project\'s research.  10,000 smallholders will be reached by the project to change their management of livestock production systems.', 'It is widely recognized that smallholders need new incentives in order to adopt different management practices, including financial resources. The role of that gender plays in adoption is of particular interest, given women’s role in livestock production more generally, and evidence that as agricultural enterprises become more profitable, women tend to lose control of them. Within Kenya and Tanzania, over the three years, the project will directly target 10,000 farmers, 50% of whom will be women and 10% of whom will be youth.', '2019', '204', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:28:26', '82', '82', ''), ('7503', null, null, null, '2015', '204', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:28:26', '82', '82', ''), ('7504', '1', 'The Kenya Dairy NAMA will be informed by the research conducted under this grant.  Targets will be set using the evidence generated.', 'It is widely recognized that smallholders need new incentives in order to adopt different management practices, including financial resources. The role of that gender plays in adoption is of particular interest, given women’s role in livestock production more generally, and evidence that as agricultural enterprises become more profitable, women tend to lose control of them. Within Kenya and Tanzania, over the three years, the project will directly target 10,000 farmers, 50% of whom will be women and 10% of whom will be youth.', '2016', '204', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:28:26', '82', '82', ''), ('7505', '1', 'we won\'t yet achieve impact in Tanzania in 2017', 'N/A', '2017', '204', '38', '69', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 09:28:26', '82', '82', ''), ('7506', '4', 'At least 4 national or subnational institutions are using equitable and transformative CSA options and CCAFS tools to plan and prioritize CSA initiatives in 4 countries (Burkina Faso, Ghana, Niger and Senegal)', 'This will be done through a reduction of inequity among actors especially women and youth in access to and control of information and technologies as most of the cropping operations are realized by these categories. The use of ICT will help as everyone will freely have access to information which is aired.', '2017', '34', '13', '53', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 10:04:27', '91', '91', ''), ('7507', '4', 'At least 4 private actors (NGOs, local rural radios, agro-dealers, etc.) are using new incentive mechanisms or At least 4 private actors (NGOs, local rural radios, agro-dealers, etc.) are using new incentive mechanisms or business models/markets that explicitly promote equitable and transformative CSA approaches along the value chain', 'This will be done through a reduction of inequity among actors especially women and youth in access to and control of information. Gender sensitive incentive and business opportunities will be developed to target the various categories of users.', '2017', '34', '14', '53', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 10:04:27', '91', '91', ''), ('7508', '1', '1 NAMA proposal will be handed in for climate finance. GHG emission reductions will have been assessed. The NAMA will focus on 22 counties with \"dairy potential\". With the partner project of the Livelihoods Fund, 30,000 farmers will be targeted.', '60% of farmers/dairy cooperative members targeted will be women. Youth (both women and men) will also be included.', '2017', '13', '38', '69', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-05 10:10:46', '905', '905', ''), ('7509', '', '', 'Gender will be one of the outcomes considered in the models and targeting.', '2017', '56', '13', '13', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 11:02:18', '73', '1', 'Outcome target has been adjusted by the PL to reflect the implications of the budget cuts.'), ('7510', '', '', 'Gender will be one of the outcomes considered in the models and targeting.', '2017', '56', '13', '53', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 11:02:18', '73', '1', 'Outcome target has been adjusted by the PL to reflect the implications of the budget cuts.'), ('7511', '', '', 'Gender will be one of the outcomes considered in the models and targeting.', '2017', '56', '13', '66', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-05 11:02:18', '73', '1', 'Outcome target has been adjusted by the PL to reflect the implications of the budget cuts.'), ('7512', '1', 'By 2017 the project will contribute towards strengthening of stakeholder platforms and the needed technical information for developing a NAMA application for implementation in the cattle sector of Colom