d to tackle any unintended negative effects on a specific target group.', '2017', '20', '13', '143', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 01:57:19', '87', '87', ''), ('7557', '', '', '', '2017', '16', '38', '149', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 13:54:40', '88', '88', ''), ('7558', '', '', '', '2017', '61', '38', '149', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:05:54', '21', '21', ''), ('7559', '', '', '', '2017', '61', '36', '148', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:05:54', '21', '21', ''), ('7560', '', '', '', '2017', '61', '13', '143', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:05:54', '21', '21', ''), ('7561', '', '', '', '2017', '61', '50', '150', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:05:54', '21', '21', ''), ('7562', '', '', '', '2017', '119', '36', '148', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:33:27', '21', '21', ''), ('7563', '', '', '', '2017', '119', '13', '143', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:33:27', '21', '21', ''), ('7564', '', '', '', '2017', '119', '50', '150', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 15:33:27', '21', '21', ''), ('7565', '5', 'At least a further 5 fertiliser/supplier/grower organisations using the improved model to inform best practice for GHG mitigation in  agriculture. A “Norma Mexicana” (Mexican Norm) for N management in wheat and maize will be developed together with the Secretaria de Economia (Secretariat of Economy of Mexico).  A stakeholder group comprising  representatives of different sectors (academics, fertilizer industry, health department, secretariat of environment, department of agriculture, etc.) will be formed to oversee the development of this Norm, which will establish recommendations on the best management practices that will minimize N losses to the environment including N2O emissions.', 'Gender and social inclusion will be taken into consideration in the analysis of barriers to uptake and trade offs.', '2017', '22', '38', '38', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-11 17:22:21', '88', '88', ''), ('7566', null, '', null, '20