stricts will use the framework developed by CCAFS to plan for CSA at district level. Planning will also mean developing baskets of options. this will be also based on info generated by project.', 'The framework will be linked with a gender framework to plan for gender interventions', '2016', '156', '13', '66', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-12 18:38:30', '271', '271', ''), ('7620', '', '', '', '2017', '156', '13', '66', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 18:38:30', '271', '271', ''), ('7621', '1', 'Internal learning in IFAD', 'Internal learning will include gender and social inclusion lessons from the research component', '2017', '127', '52', '25', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 18:50:17', '131', '131', ''), ('7622', '1', 'Research in East and West Africa has enabled the research team to bring in additional funding and to embed index insurance in an agricultural initiative in another part of the world. This may well be Central America where CIMMYT and IRI are already working.', 'The project will link with CCAFS-supported index insurance work in Ghana to look at the gender implications of index insurance', '2017', '51', '36', '68', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 19:05:11', '100', '100', ''), ('7623', '', '', '', '2017', '131', '38', '38', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 20:19:07', '50', '996', ''), ('7624', '', '', '', '2017', '131', '39', '39', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 20:19:07', '50', '996', ''), ('7625', '0', 'none', 'none', '2017', '18', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 22:51:51', '52', '52', ''), ('7626', null, null, null, '2019', '18', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-12 22:51:51', '52', '52', ''), ('7627', '0', null, null, '2015', '18', '39', '90', '0.00', 'none', 'none', '1', '2015-11-12 22:51:51', '52', '52', ''), ('7628', '50000', 'For the Ha Tinh province the project output will provide viable plans for managing the land in the two provinces under consideration in ways that promote economic growth and do not increase GHG emissions compared to the baseline. The baseline emissions are based on a plausible development of each province based on domestic growth plans and exogenous economic forces generated by prices changes and demand for food products.', 'We do not target gender issues in this project although it is possible that we will learn if gender is a barrier in the adoption favorable practices.', '2016', '18', '39', '90', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-12 22:51:51', '52', '52', ''), ('7629', '100000', 'For the Ha Tinh and Yen Bai provinces, the project output will provide viable plans for managing the land in the two provinces under consideration in ways that promote economic growth and do not increase GHG emissions compared to the baseline. The baseline emissions are based on a plausible development of each province based on domestic growth plans and exogenous economic forces generated by prices changes and demand for food products.', 'We do not target gender issues in this project although it is possible that we will learn if gender is a barrier in the adoption favorable practices.', '2017', '18', '39', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-12 22:51:51', '52', '52', ''), ('7630', '3', 'Results of scenario analysis will be used by local authorities at subnational level to tailor the mitigation actions plan for the Andean highlands agriculture (2014-30).\r\n\r\nContinued stakeholder engagement and regional assessment allow policy makers to take decision based on information and recommendation from CIAT. This increases the ownership of the livestock NAMA and improves the skills in national authorities to generate feasible NAMA (2014-31).\r\n\r\nLivestock and Coffee NAMA being implemented based on continuously up dated CCAFS science.', 'CCAFS contributes input on gender incorporation for one policy (NAMA/NAP/other climate risk prevention/response protocols) draft (2014-29).', '2017', '2', '38', '121', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 02:02:42', '66', '66', ''), ('7631', '1', 'Skills of subnational authorities and information on climate change science facilitated by CCAFS allow inclusion of regional consideration in NAP (2014-32).', 'CCAFS contributes input on gender incorporation for one policy (NAMA/NAP/other climate risk prevention/response protocols) draft (2014-29).', '2017', '2', '50', '126', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 02:02:42', '66', '66', ''), ('7632', '0', 'The project does not address this outcome anymore, due to Bioversity International discontinuing activities under this FP project.', 'The project does not address this outcome anymore, due to Bioversity International discontinuing activities under this FP project.', '2017', '2', '52', '126', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 02:02:42', '66', '66', ''), ('7633', '3', 'Develop at least 3 policies at national/sub national levels  to prioritise climate smart agriculture intervention this will lead to 1 million farmers will implement Climate Smart Agriculture practices and technologies.', 'We have analyzed existing CSA policies & programs in South Asian countries to understand their implications on women and smallholders. Further, we are actively trying to capture preferences of women farmers in our research on understanding farmers\' preferences and willingness to pay for CS technologies and practices. This research will inform policy-makers on how to make CSA policies and programs more inclusive and sensitive to gender issues in agriculture.', '2017', '60', '50', '150', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 04:47:57', '77', '878', ''), ('7634', '1', 'N/A', 'N/A', '2017', '5', '38', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 07:38:07', '864', '864', ''), ('7635', '1', 'N/A', 'N/A', '2017', '5', '39', '90', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-13 07:38:07', '864', '864', ''), ('7636', '1', 'Plan for selected provinces in Vietnam developed', 'Gender aspects will be fully integrated in the plan by continuous involvement of women farmers', '2017', '21', '38', '90', null, nu