, null, '0', '2015-11-17 17:26:43', '176', '178', ''), ('7703', '', '', '', '2017', '45', '36', '148', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-17 23:08:47', '98', '98', ''), ('7707', '6', 'Three countries will adopt two policy measures to implement the ITPGRFA/MLS in harmony with the CBD/Nagoya Protocol from the following list: Ministerial decrees confirming national crop diversity included in multilateral system of access and benefit sharing under the ITPGRFA; New/revised national decrees/regulations/legislation on access and benefit sharing under the CBD/Nagoya Protocol to make space of the operation of the ITPGRFA; New/revised national decrees/regulations/legislation empowering actors to share materials under the ITPGRFA; National multi-stakeholder platforms established for coordinated ABS policy development and capacity building; Guidelines issued by competent authorities on how to operate the ITPGRFA and NP for climate change adaptation.', null, '2019', '66', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-18 09:59:22', '243', '68', ''), ('7708', '4', null, null, '2015', '66', '50', '24', '12.00', 'Perspectives, interests and needs of various social actors in relation to the ITPGRFA/MLS and related policies and laws were identified and the degree of direct and active involvement of women/men farmers in national policy processes assesed. National decision makers made some efforts to take differences into consideration in policy/law formulation.', '- Rwanda: Confirmation of PGRFA in MLS\r\n- Bhutan: Ministerial decree appointing competent authority (CA decree) \r\n- Costa Rica: Directriz Normativa consensuada entre el punto focal del TIRFAA y CONAREFI (Ministerio de Agricultura) y CONAGEBIO (Ministerio de Ambiente); confirmation of PGRFA in MLS; CA decree\r\n-Guatemala: CA decree; confirmation of PGRFA in MLS \r\n- Nepal: New Agrobiodiversity Policy; revised NBSAP \r\n- Uganda: Memorandum of Understanding, National Environment (Access to genetic resources and benefit sharing) Regulations, and Temporary procedure for accessing plant genetic resources for food and agriculture; confirmation of PGRFA in MLS; CA decree\r\n- Burkina Faso: CA decree', '1', '2015-11-18 09:59:22', '243', '68', ''), ('7709', '1', 'Adopt policy to create community seed banks as part of sustainable use and climate change adaptation strategy', 'N/A', '2016', '66', '50', '24', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-18 09:59:22', '243', '68', ''), ('7710', '4', 'National and subnational policies and implementation mechanisms put in place to regulate genetic resources access and benefit sharing, and to empower national policy actors (including communities) to acquire genetic resources for climate change adaptation. [for 2017-2018, which is final year of the project]', 'State recognition of local community right to participate in decision making regarding the conservation and exploitation of genetic resources. Local community develop access and benefit sharing protocols. Women included in local community committees to consider access applications.', '2017', '66', '50', '24', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-18 09:59:22', '243', '68', ''), ('7711', '', '', '', '2017', '67', '50', '24', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-19 02:03:32', '153', '153', ''), ('7712', '', '', '', '2017', '67', '52', '25', null, null, null, '0', '2015-11-19 02:03:32', '153', '153', ''), ('7713', '', '', '', '2019', '217', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-19 06:05:57', '153', '153', ''), ('7714', null, null, null, '2015', '217', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-19 06:05:57', '153', '153', ''), ('7715', '2', 'SPC and FFA', 'All data collection and analyses gender differentiated', '2016', '217', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-19 06:05:57', '153', '153', ''), ('7716', '', '', '', '2017', '217', '52', '25', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-19 06:05:57', '153', '153', ''), ('7717', '', '', '', '2019', '238', '36', '89', null, null, null, '1', '2015-11-19 10:19:21', '108', '108'